Notes: We’re low actuation force key switches, but feel free to use another actuation force, in the same 5E series or 5G* You’ll need to modify the panels in consequence if you use a 5G series.

We’re using encoders without detent and without switch, T18. The shortest available in this series. Use PEC11R-4015F-N0024 if you want D_Shaft terminaison. Find a reference in the same series if you want to use a different length.
Adjust height depending on the thickness of the panel etc. Try multiple heights eventually. These caps fit the 5E series ONLY.
Use what you want, adjust the choice of encoders in consequence (T18 or D-Shaft)
